OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,Fin the north and along Irish Sea
OL,7,Fcoasts with some patchy drizzle. Dry
OL,8,Felsewhere with clear spells. A mild
OL,9,Fnight for most, although locally
OL,10,Fchilly in sheltered spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother grey start with
OL,13,Ffurther rain across the north, which
OL,14,Fmay turn heavier and more persistent
OL,15,Flater. Some sunny spells developing
OL,16,Facross the south and feeling mild for
OL,17,Fall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
